#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksirk;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item opens a dialog that allows you to:"
